

                         toffmo: The OFFice MOtivator


REQUERIMENTS

  Python (http://www.python.org)


BUILD AND INSTALL

  $ make
  $ sudo make install
  or
  $ sudo make install DESTDIR=/path/to/dir


USAGE

  toffmo <options>

  Where options are:
  -h, --help           Show this help information
  -V, --version        Show version information
  --conf=CONFIG        Use alternate config file


BUGS AND REPORTS

